{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BlueSpark}}
'''A_BlueSpark'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns two {{Class|Sorcerer2FXSpark}} actors and gives them different random horizontal velocities between -2 and +2 on both X and Y axes, and between 1 and 2 on the Z axis.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Sorcerer2FX1}} and derived classes.

